===Etymology===
{{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}} considers this a {{m|und|*-t}} derivation of {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*nwe||warm}}, whence also {{cog|my|နွေး||warm; lukewarm}}, {{m|my|နွှေး||to warm something; to revise}}. However, {{zh-ref|Schuessler (2024)}} notes many cases where medial {{m|und|*-w-}} is deleted after non-velar initials and before {{m|und|*e}} and seems to relegate the above etymology to {{och-l|熱|hot}} instead; he instead compares {{och-l|爇|tr=*n(i)ot}} to {{cog|bo|རྔོད||to fry; to roast}}, though this is not without problems either.

Either way, {{och-l|熱|hot}} may still be related ({{zh-ref|Karlgren, 1956}}).

